cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.DC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on semantic parsing and semantic role labeling for learner Chinese. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is also likely as the paper evaluates the performance of different SRL systems on learner data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper explores the use of large-scale L2-L1 parallel data to enhance SRL for learner texts. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are less likely but still possible categories as they may involve similar techniques and methods used in the paper.
